addRangeTupleSlice

public void addRangeTupleSlice(double[] slice)
The first tuple slice (dimension) added is assumed to be the domain, whose values must be in sorted ascending order. Subsequent slices are assumed to be components of an n-tuple range. See getRangeTupleSlice(int).
